                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. shows traces of extensive use and was rebound.&#xD;
Quires II was added later.&#xD;
The bifolio with the miniature (fols. 90-91) might orginate from a different codex.&#xD;
The Ms. seems to be incomplete as in Text I-4 the miracles are numbered until 123 whereas 134 miracles are mentioned in the subscriptio on fol. 181rb. &#xD;
Fol. 18 was cut, only the portion with the text is preserved.  &#xD;
Fol. 145 was added later, sewn onto the stub of fol. 138 (quire XIX).&#xD;
Holes or tears amended on fols. 12, 51, 54, 99, 116, 123, 148, 159, 164, 167, 168.</condition>
