                     <origDate notBefore="1598" notAfter="1674" instant="false">According to the colophon, the Ms. was written in 250 year of mercy (= 1674 A.D.). It could be dated back also to 1598 A.D. (if the date is calculated according to the cicle of martyrs); this earlier date would better match the palaeographic features attested for hand a. &#xD;
